Reasoning: This paper uses natural language processing techniques to automatically appraise the credibility of webpages related to vaccination shared on Twitter. It involves text classification using machine learning algorithms such as random forest, support vector machines, and recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other possible sub-categories include cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
